G. S. Ellithorpe, Appellant, v. Glenn E. Holmes, Appellee.Gen. No. 40,511.

(Abstract of Decision.)

Heard in second division, first district, this court at December term, 1938;opinion filed May 28, 1940;rehearing denied June 12, 1940.Laurence M. Fine, for appellant; Sonnensehein, Berkson, Lautmann, Levinson & Morse, for appellee; Herbert M. Lautmann and Henry L. Kohn, of counsel. Opinion by Justice Scanlan.

“Not to be published in full.”
